ing, high-tech environment filled with neon-lit paths and mesmerizing graphics. The game mechanics are designed to test and enhance your coordination and problem-solving skills. Each level presents a unique maze-like track, teeming with hurdles that require quick thinking and precise movements to overcome.\nKey Features\n\n    Dynamic Spheres: Master the control of highly responsive spheres, each with unique attributes and abilities that you can unlock and upgrade as you progress.\n\n    Intricate Tracks: Navigate through a variety of complex and beautifully designed tracks. Each track offers different challenges, from narrow passages to moving barriers and beyond.", "short_description": "Orb Conquest: The Ultimate VR Experience\n\nDive into the exhilarating world of \"Orb Conquest,\" a cutting-edge VR game that challenges your precision, reflexes, and strategic thinking. Set in a futuristic realm where you control dynamic spheres, your mission is to navigate these spheres through intricate tracks and lines, overcoming a series of increasingly complex obstacles and challenges."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/orbconquest/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "SGag2426 Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/orbconquest", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_mo